commit.message: Fix insufficient spacing after "Needs work" on MSW
Merge branch 'devel/boost-modular'

Update Boost to 1.84.0, use submodules

Switch to using a git submodule that includes the respective modular
Boost repositories of libraries (transitively) used by Poedit.
GHA: Setup parallel submodule fetching
Remove vendored copy of Boost
Set consistent C++ standard in Xcode and VS projects

Remove Lucene++ dependency on boost::regex

Remove the one remaining dependency on boost::regex inherited from
Lucene++. This only affects Mac and Windows builds.

Lucene++: don't build some unneeded parts

Omit some files that aren't used by Poedit from build. This slightly
reduces the number of Boost sub-library dependencies.
Move Boost projects to deps/custom_build

Build Boost as single static library

Don't split it into multiple libraries like upstream does, build a
single static library instead. This simplifies adding/removing stuff and
has no practical impact, because it is a static archive anyway.
Merge branch 'devel/sparkle-2.2'
Merge branch '3.4'
Fix/improve support for signing Inno Setup distributions

Don't use Sparkle's deprecated SUUpdater API

Rewrite Sparkle code w/o the now-deprecated SUUpdater singleton. This
makes the code more explicit and actually closer to its WinSparkle
counterpart.
Remove no longer used PoeditApp::NativeMacAppData
Refactor Sparkle updates checking to its own file
Fix $(IntDir) with Visual Studio 17.9

Update Sparkle to 2.2, switch to using SPM

Update Sparkle version to 2.2 (the latest version that doesn't require
EdDSA). While doing so, switch to using Swift Package Manager in Xcode
instead of a submodule for Sparkle.
Xcode 14.3 settings updates
Don't prevent the manager from showing if 1 file is bad
Merge branch 'devel/upgrade-to-wx-3.2'

Workaround wx-3.2 issues with translation lookup

Special-case some problematic cases until wx-3.2.x includes the fixes
from https://github.com/wxWidgets/wxWidgets/pull/24297

Better workaround for wx-3.2

GHA: Make git revlist --count work

Builds on Windows and macOS require git rev-list to properly embed
full version number. Extend fetched history, using blobless checkout to
reduce the impact.
GHA: Pin Xcode version for CI build
GHA: update actions versions to use node20
gexecute.cpp compilation fix

Fix ARB @@locale parsing to use locale, not tag

Poedit incorrectly parsed the @@locale value as a BCP47 tag and wrote it
as one too. This was incorrect, the value is indeed a locale, using '_'
and not '-' as language/country delimiter.

Stricter checking of uloc_forLanguageTag() results

Even though the function is supposed to return error code in status,
sometimes it returns U_ZERO_ERROR there, but the resulting string is
empty. Check for that case explicitly too.

Fix accidental conversions through wxString

Fix code that accidentally performed std::string to wxString to
std::wstring conversions "thanks" to implicit conversion in wxString.
Correctly scale Localazy project icons on MSW
